data.description: SELLER VERY MOTIVATED!!!  Amazingly beautiful 2 story condo with open floor plan. Extremely nice and clean from top to bottom with high quality finishes thru out the place. New kitchen cabinets, stainless steel appliances including dishwasher, granite counter tops, beautiful backsplash, custom ceiling lighting in the kitchen, food pantry area, kitchen dining area, recessed lighting thru out, 2 large bedrooms upstairs and remodeled bathroom with walk in closet. It's located in a beautiful community that shows pride of ownership for everyone.  The community has a playground and is a short walk to park and White Oak Elementary and conveniently located close to shopping with easy freeway access. HOA includes trash and water.    This property is being sold with contingency of seller's finding new home of choice.
